###Options:
A.  Sodium bicarbonate  {NaHCO3}
B.  Calcium carbonate {CaCO3}
C.  Aluminum hydroxide {Al(OH)3}
D.  Magnesium hydroxide {Mg(OH)2}
E.  Calcium hydroxide {Ca(OH)2}

###Answer:
